?s=%D8%B9%D9%8E%D9%84%D9%8E%D9%91%D9%84%D9%8E"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to give to drink a second time"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to divert, to busy, to occupy, to distract, to entertain"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to explain, to account for; to reason","examples":[{"text":"مَا هِيَ ٱلْعَوَامِلُ ٱلَّتِي تُعَلِّلُ أَسْبَابَ هٰذِهِ ٱلنَّتَائِجِ ٱلسَّيِّئَةِ؟","english":"What factors explain these disappointing results?"},{"text":"كَيْفَ تُعَلِّلُونَ حَقِيقَةً أَنَّكُمْ نَجَوْتُمْ فِي كُلِّ مَرَّةٍ؟","english":"How do you account for the fact that you survive each time?"}]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ʕal.la.la/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n30132","headword_ar":"عَلَلٌ","root":"El","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eal~N","text_ar":"عَلٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[both mentioned in the first paragraph as inf. ns.] The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"second draught:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a drinking after drinking, uninterruptedly:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or the former signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a second drinking;"},{"kind":"text","text":"one says"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalalN baEoda nahalK","text_ar":"عَلَلٌ بَعْدَ نَهَلٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a second drinking after a first drinking"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S, O:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a drinking after drinking:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) and the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"second watering"},{"kind":"text","text":"of camels; the first being termed the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nahal","text_ar":"نَهَل"},{"kind":"text","text":": (As, TA:) these two terms are also similarly used in relation to suckling: and one of the unknown poets says,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"vum~a A@novanaY mino baEodi *aA faSal~aY\n                      \n                     ↓ \n      EalaY Aln~abiY~i nahalFA waEal~aA"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Then he turned,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"turned away"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"back, after that, and blessed the Prophet a first time and a second time"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b2-  Also, the former, Food"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that has been eaten."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Kr, TA.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nahalN","text_ar":"نَهَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":["K","S","O","Msb","As","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n30133","headword_ar":"عُلُلٌ","root":"El","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuloEulN","text_ar":"عُلْعُلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}